e>特鲁多总理表示，加拿大考虑对“极端主义”以色列约旦河西岸定居者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/canada-considers-sanctions-on-extremist-israeli-west-bank-settlers-pm-trudeau-says/0000018d-6b02-d971-a38f-7bb2dc580000</link><description>加拿大总理表示，约旦河西岸的暴力行为是绝对不可接受的，该地区的和平、稳定以及两国解决方案的道路都受到威胁。巴勒斯坦平民</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 18:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/canada-considers-sanctions-on-extremist-israeli-west-bank-settlers-pm-trudeau-says/0000018d-6b02-d971-a38f-7bb2dc580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全内阁考虑与哈马斯达成为期142天的人质协议和停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-cabinet-mulls-proposed-142-day-hostage-deal-cease-fire-with-hamas/0000018d-6ac2-dd6e-a98d-fee220890000</link><description>一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，该计划提议在停火期间每天释放一名人质，但该计划遭到了内阁成员的严厉批评，他们反对延长停火期限和分阶段释放人质。极右翼部长本格维尔表示，这样的协议将为哈马斯提供氧气。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 17:43:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-cabinet-mulls-proposed-142-day-hostage-deal-cease-fire-with-hamas/0000018d-6ac2-dd6e-a98d-fee220890000</guid></item><item><title>管理战后加沙将需要许多为哈马斯工作的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/running-postwar-gaza-will-require-many-who-worked-for-hamas/0000018d-6a3e-d4f1-a18d-fe7e810d0000</link><description>除非以色列直接控制加沙，否则它将不得不允许巴勒斯坦权力机构雇用哈马斯雇用的数万名公务员。停火可能是让巴勒斯坦权力机构掌握权力的机会</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/running-postwar-gaza-will-require-many-who-worked-for-hamas/0000018d-6a3e-d4f1-a18d-fe7e810d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯表示正在研究以色列人质协议提案，致力于永久停火要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/hamas-says-its-studying-hostage-deal-proposal-committed-to-permanent-cease-fire-demand/0000018d-6a34-d971-a38f-7bb6bb380000</link><description>贝鲁特哈马斯高级官员奥萨马·哈姆丹表示，该组织要求释放数千名巴勒斯坦囚犯，并永久停火 — — 这一条件与埃及和以色列官员提出的多阶段提案相矛盾、卡塔尔和美国</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/hamas-says-its-studying-hostage-deal-proposal-committed-to-permanent-cease-fire-demand/0000018d-6a34-d971-a38f-7bb6bb380000</guid></item><item><title>资料来源：沙特向以色列开放，绕过对巴勒斯坦国的约束性步骤，以争取美国国防协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/saudis-open-to-israel-bypassing-binding-steps-for-palestinian-state-in-u-s-defense-bid/0000018d-6a2c-d971-a38f-7bbe1bcf0000</link><description>在美国领导的沙特阿拉伯和以色列之间的正常化努力因加沙战争陷入停滞后，官员们表示，利雅得不会坚持以色列采取具体步骤建立巴勒斯坦国，而是会接受对两国解决方案的政治承诺</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 15:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/saudis-open-to-israel-bypassing-binding-steps-for-palestinian-state-in-u-s-defense-bid/0000018d-6a2c-d971-a38f-7bbe1bcf0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡是个破布？绝对地。在以色列，他并不孤单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-a-rag-absolutely-and-in-israel-hes-not-alone/0000018d-698d-dd6e-a98d-fdafe6360000</link><description>用希伯来语的同义词来说，谁是聪明人？如果问 1000 万以色列人，简短的回答是“每个人”——当然，以色列政治中的白痴数量也在不断增加</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 13:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-a-rag-absolutely-and-in-israel-hes-not-alone/0000018d-698d-dd6e-a98d-fdafe6360000</guid></item><item><title>拜登针对暴力以色列定居者的行政命令改变了游戏规则</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-02/ty-article/.premium/bidens-executive-order-on-violent-israeli-settlers-is-a-game-changer/0000018d-699e-dd6e-a98d-fdbe10460000</link><description>该命令可能会不可逆转地改变约旦河西岸定居者的事业，并为可能制裁以色列官员奠定基础，尽管一些批评者认为这是对拜登以色列-加沙政策持谨慎态度的民主党人的口头承诺</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 12:51:20 GMT</pu